bilingual.source: My friend wants to be an engineer.
bilingual.target: 我的朋友想成为一名工程师。

bilingual.source: And you wanted me to be an engineer!
bilingual.target: 你想让我成为一名工程师！

bilingual.source: You must study maths to be an engineer.
bilingual.target: 你必须学习数学才能成为工程师。

bilingual.source: The engineer made the robot clean the windows of the tall building.
bilingual.target: 工程师让机器人清洁高楼的窗户。

bilingual.source: As a computer engineer, there's always a new challenge just around the corner!
bilingual.target: 作为一名计算机工程师，总是有新的挑战在眼前！
我的哥哥是一名工程师。

bilingual.source: He works as an engineer in the mina.

list.abstract: Engineer（英 [ˌendʒɪˈnɪə]，美 [ˌendʒɪˈnɪr]），英语单词，作名词用，为工程师；技师；机械师。作动词用，为设计；制造；精心安排。短语搭配有civil engineer（土木工程师），例句为“It was designed by an English engineer.（它是由一位英国工程师设计的）”。 Engineer名词类近义词有gineer、sapper，及物动词类近义词有design、style、project等，不及物动词类近义词有project、design，名词形式为engine、engineering，复数形式为engineers。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm an engineer. Most engineers don't bother with a PhD.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我是工程师，工程师通常不需要博士学位。

yingyinNormal.en: Howard doesn't. He's only an engineer.
yingyinNormal.zh: 霍华德用不到那个，他只不过是个工程师。

yingyinNormal.en: I was covering my engineer, so he shot him straight through me. A Soviet slag, no rifling. Byebye bikinis.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我挡着工程师，他的子弹穿过我，击中工程师，前苏联子弹，没有弹道，再见了比基尼。

yingyinNormal.en: Don't you think I should answer the engineering questions? I am an engineer.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你难道不觉得应该由我来回答工程问题吗？我是个工程师。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm just trying to help you. You're in my home now. I'm an engineer. My name is Cade Yeager.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我只是想帮你，这里是我家我是工程师，叫凯德伊格。

yingyinNormal.en: You're joking. I am a horny engineer Leonard. I never joke about math or sex.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你开玩笑吧。我是个性饥渴的工程师，莱纳德，我从不拿数学和性开玩笑。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, I'm a scientist by training. Really? You're a physicist? Better. I'm an engineer.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我是被培训出来的科学家。是吗？你是物理学家吗？比那强，我是工程师。

yingyinNormal.en: That's a pretty cool idea. Yeah. It's great you're here. I'd love to get an engineer's opinion.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这个主意真不错。你在这儿真是太好了，我很想听听工程师的建议。

yingyinNormal.en: Five years ago I was escorting a nuclear engineer out of Iran, somebody shot at my tires near Odessa.
yingyinNormal.zh: 五年前，我护送一个核物理工程师离开中东，有人在敖德萨附近打爆了我的车胎。

yingyinNormal.en: I could also be the engineer who builds the crossbow that kills Sheldon. You still might get on a magazine.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我也可以成为那个造出一把弩弓用来射杀谢尔顿的工程师。你仍然可能因此上杂志。

yingyinNormal.en: Anyway as angry as I was with him leaving, building this stuff is probably what led me to become an engineer.
yingyinNormal.zh: 言归正传，虽然我对他的离去还有怨气，但我大概就是因为搭过这些模型才去当了工程师。

yingyinNormal.en: Howard, this is big science. You could be the engineer who builds the equipment that puts us on the cover of magazines.
yingyinNormal.zh: 霍华德，这可是重大科研项目，你可以成为那个组建仪器的工程师，我们能因此上杂志封面呢。

yingyinNormal.en: I think it is about Sheldon. How many times has he made fun of Howard for being an engineer? Going to MIT? His magic?
yingyinNormal.zh: 这事的罪魁祸首就是谢尔顿。他嘲笑霍华德是工程师都多少次了？还笑他麻省理工的学位和他的魔术？

yingyinNormal.en: Engineer Tim Sweitzer is working to change the shipyard by using the same approach as Volkswagen, a philosophy called "lean manufacturing."
yingyinNormal.zh: 工程师提姆·斯威兹 正在改变这一船坞，用着和大众一样的方法，哲学家称之为精实生产。

yingyinNormal.en: And one of Dawson's first acts as governor was to approve a $12 million grant for that man, Jerrod Wilkins, software engineer, 41 years old, recently divorced.
yingyinNormal.zh: 道森身为州长的第一步就是批款一千两百万给那个人，杰罗德·威尔金斯，软件工程师，四十一岁，刚刚离婚。

yingyinNormal.en: Now, I'm sure this makes a very capable starter kit, but the everyday person, the kind of person that's not an engineer, or in a computer club like you。
yingyinNormal.zh: 至少现在是，我知道你们做了个入门辅助工具包，但是大部分人他们不是什么工程师也不是什么电脑俱乐部的成员，比如说你们

yingyinNormal.en: Oh. All right. I doubt anyone would risk the stiff penalties for impersonating a federal officer just to ask questions about a minor league engineer with an unresolved oedipal complex. Thank you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好吧，我想没人会冒着假扮联邦政府探员的重罪来问几个关于一个患有强烈恋母情结的小工程师的问题。谢谢。

yingyinNormal.en: Granted, you're just an engineer, but that doesn't mean you might not someday build a geegaw or a thingamabob that may get you a "thank you" in someone else's Nobel Prize acceptance speech.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我知道你只是个工程师，但是这并不意味着你不会某天做出一个小把戏或者小玩意儿能让别人在诺贝尔奖的获奖演说里送你一句"感谢某人"呀。

yingyinNormal.en: Which is something I realized when I was viewing Earth from the deck of the International Space Station, where I spent two months as a payload specialist, a job I was qualified for because I'm an MIT-trained engineer.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我意识到这点时是在遥远的外太空，当时我从国际空间站的甲板上瞭望地球，我以科学宇航员的身份待了两个月，这份工作我完全能胜任，因为我是麻省理工培养出来的工程师。

yingyinNormal.en: This train thing worked out better than I thought. He's home studying the engineer's manual.
yingyinNormal.zh: 火车的吸引力比我想象中还大，他现在在家学习火车驾驶员手册呢。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: Their teams of <highlight>engineers</highlight> stayed on, making them two of the many "acqui-hires".
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他们的工程师团队留了下来，使他们成为众多“新雇员”中的两个。

examination_example.sentence: Crop pickers, violinists, construction workers, entrepreneurs, <highlight>engineers</highlight>, home health-care aides and physicists are among today's birds of passage.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 摘庄稼的人、小提琴手、建筑工人、企业家、工程师、家庭保健助理和物理学家都是当今的热门人物。

examination_example.sentence: The Victorian author Samuel Smiles wrote Self-Help as a catalogue of the worthy lives of <highlight>engineers</highlight>, industrialists and explorers.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 维多利亚时代的作家塞缪尔·斯迈尔斯写了《自助》一书，列举了工程师、实业家和探险家的宝贵生活。

sense_info_list.en: design and build a machine or structure

examination_example.sentence: That's the problem with a social cure <highlight>engineered</highlight>: in the real world we insist on choosing our own friends.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这就是社会治疗设计的问题所在:在现实世界中，我们坚持选择自己的朋友。

sense_info_list.en: to change the genetic structure of something

examination_example.sentence: Humanity has the necessary agro-technological tools to eradicate hunger, from genetically <highlight>engineered</highlight> crops to artificial fertilizers.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 人类拥有消除饥饿的必要农业技术工具，从转基因作物到人造肥料。

sense_info_list.en: skillfully or artfully arrange for an event or situation to occur
